snippet: Milos Raonic easily advanced to the Rogers Cup quarterfinals in front of his home fans, routing American qualifier Jared Donaldson 6-2, 6-3 on Thursday night....
lead_paragraph: Milos Raonic easily advanced to the Rogers Cup quarterfinals in front of his home fans, routing American qualifier Jared Donaldson 6-2, 6-3 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Canada's Milos Raonic Reaches Toronto Quarterfinals
headline.main: Canada's Milos Raonic Reaches Toronto Quarterfinals
